```plantuml
@startuml andersonkmi_credit-card-bindb-service-aws
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "API Gateway" as APIGW #lightgrey

rectangle "AWS Lambda Functions" as Lambda #lightgreen {
  rectangle "CSV Ingestion" as CSVIngestion
  rectangle "Data Transformation" as DataTransformation
  rectangle "Store in DynamoDB" as StoreDynamoDB
}

rectangle "AWS S3" as S3 #aliceblue

rectangle "AWS SQS" as SQS #lightyellow

rectangle "Amazon DynamoDB" as DynamoDB #lightsteelblue

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> APIGW : Invoke API

' API Gateway interactions
APIGW --> CSVIngestion : Trigger CSV ingestion

' AWS Lambda interactions
CSVIngestion --> S3 : Read CSV files
CSVIngestion --> SQS : Send messages for processing

SQS --> DataTransformation : Trigger data transformation
DataTransformation --> StoreDynamoDB : Processed data

StoreDynamoDB --> DynamoDB : Store processed BIN data
@enduml
```